<h2> Import databse from sql file </h2>
in console: <br>
[root@virtualdev ~]# <b> wget http://virtual.ibg/ina/192.168.155.7-ALL_DATABASES.sql.tar.gz </b><br>
[root@virtualdev ~]# <b> tar -zxvf 192.168.155.7-ALL_DATABASES.sql.tar.gz </b><br>
[root@virtualdev ~]# <b> cd data2/datawarehouse/current/192.168.155.7-ALL_DATABASES.sql </b> <br>
[root@virtualdev ~]# <b> mysql -u root -pibgpass < 192.168.155.7-ALL_DATABASES.sql </b> <br>

<BR> WARNING: IMPORTING DATABASE FROM FULL BACKUP IS OVERRIDING THE MYSQL USER/PASSWORD TABLE! <BR>

<hr>


<h2> Change mysql root password </h2>
in console: <br>
[root@virtualdev ~]# <b> mysql </b> <br>
<b> UPDATE mysql.user SET Password=PASSWORD('ibgpass') WHERE User='root'; </b> <br>
<b> FLUSH PRIVILEGES; </b> <br>
<b> exit; </b> <br>

<hr>

