<h2> Git ftp </h2>
Install: <br> 
$ git clone https://github.com/git-ftp/git-ftp.git <br>
$ cd git-ftp/ <br>
$ make install <br>
<br>
Usage: <br>
$ cd project <br>
$ git config git-ftp.user USER <br>
$ git config git-ftp.password PASSWORD <br>
$ git config git-ftp.url PROTOCOL://IP:PORT/PROJECTDIR/ <br>
(example: git config git-ftp.url ftp://192.168.15.22:21/gitftptest/) <br>
$ git ftp init (Only once) <br>
$ git ftp push <br>
<br>
<b> documentation : <a href="https://github.com/git-ftp/git-ftp/blob/develop/man/git-ftp.1.md"> https://github.com/git-ftp/git-ftp/blob/develop/man/git-ftp.1.md </a> </b> <br>

